data.description: SELLERS WILL CONTRIBUTE $10,500 TO BUYER FOR 2-1 BUYDOWN OR ANY WAY MONEY WITH ACCEPCTABLE OFFER !!! CLOSE TO PENSACOLA NAS and BEACHES! Gorgeous 4 bedroom, 3.5 bathroom home with 2 car garage in Berkshire Estates! The beautifully maintained and updated home has much to offer. As you enter the home, the open concept first floor welcomes you to the spacious living room with LVP wood look flooring, ceiling fan, and plenty of windows for lots of natural light. You are then guided to the dining area with new lighting and room for large table to entertain family and guests. The spacious kitchen has been tastefully updated with gorgeous granite countertops and island breakfast bar with waterfall countertops, tumbled subway tile backsplash, new lighting and more! Side by side refrigerator, smooth top range, microwave, dishwasher, and pantry. Just off the kitchen is a powder room half bathroom for guests. The master bedroom is located on the first floor with plenty of room for a king bed. Enjoy the master bedroom walk-in closet and large master bathroom with double vanity, lined closet, and shower. As you enter the second floor of the home, you are greeted by a massive flex room currently being used as a media room for the family to enjoy. The three additional bedrooms and two additional full bathrooms are all on the 2nd floor. Bedroom 2 & 3 are separated by a nice Jack & Jill bathroom with tub/shower. Bedroom 4 has its own full bathroom. The indoor laundry room can also be found on the second floor for added convenience. This home offer a two car garage with auto opener. The driveway has been extended for extra parking. The front yard has pretty ornamentals in the landscaping and a Craftsman style covered front porch for that curb appeal. The exterior of the home already has gutters in place, so no need to add those! The privacy fenced back yard is all about the outdoor living spaces. This home offers 3 great out door spaces to enjoy where most homes are lucky to have one. First, the 17x9 screen porch is perfect for entertaining and is wired for TV. Second, 17x10 open deck is a great outdoor space to enjoy. Third, the 20x10 paver patio is an enjoyable extended space for those extra guests while making memories! The peaceful back yard also offers a privacy fence with two gates and shed. This great home is close to schools, shopping, beaches, downtown Pensacola and the Pensacola NAS, and would make an easy commute to work. Don't let your opportunity to own this beautiful home slip by...schedule your showing TODAY!!!
